1
00:00:16,128 --> 00:00:17,407
I spent so much time drawing this.

2
00:00:17,527 --> 00:00:19,027
I'll draw another one next time.

3
00:00:19,228 --> 00:00:20,648
If you do this again, I won't talk to you.

4
00:00:23,947 --> 00:00:24,727
Do you like it?

5
00:00:26,328 --> 00:00:28,988
Maybe I can help you.

6
00:01:07,407 --> 00:01:08,647
Since the facts are clear,

7
00:01:09,147 --> 00:01:10,367
for the survival of the group,

8
00:01:10,727 --> 00:01:12,367
I propose to start voting now

9
00:01:12,367 --> 00:01:13,528
to reorganize the board of directors,

10
00:01:13,848 --> 00:01:16,587
and I will temporarily take over the duties of the chairman

11
00:01:16,848 --> 00:01:17,308
until...

12
00:01:17,507 --> 00:01:17,988
Wait.

13
00:01:20,847 --> 00:01:23,687
I did all of this.

14
00:01:24,187 --> 00:01:24,888
Wu Xi,

15
00:01:25,788 --> 00:01:27,347
this isn't the place for you to act recklessly.

16
00:01:32,567 --> 00:01:35,608
Zhi Mei, I was possessed by the devil.

17
00:01:35,967 --> 00:01:37,467
I used Zhang Wei's connections

18
00:01:37,847 --> 00:01:38,987
to manipulate overseas accounts

19
00:01:39,228 --> 00:01:41,008
and the trust fund. It was all me.

20
00:01:41,407 --> 00:01:42,127
Wu Xi,

21
00:01:42,707 --> 00:01:43,888
do you know the consequences

22
00:01:43,888 --> 00:01:44,668
of falsely confessing?

23
00:01:45,648 --> 00:01:46,648
As long as we remarry,

24
00:01:46,847 --> 00:01:48,067
I'll be your legal husband.

25
00:01:48,528 --> 00:01:50,327
I'll take all the blame.

26
00:01:54,067 --> 00:01:54,927
I'll turn myself in.

27
00:01:55,047 --> 00:01:55,788
I'll make amends.

28
00:01:56,047 --> 00:01:57,748
I'll take all the blame.

29
00:01:58,008 --> 00:01:59,127
As long as you're safe,

30
00:01:59,207 --> 00:02:00,248
I'll do anything, Zhimei.

31
00:02:00,248 --> 00:02:00,648
Wu Xi,

32
00:02:01,207 --> 00:02:02,288
the law is not a game.

33
00:02:02,948 --> 00:02:04,707
You can't just take the blame.

34
00:02:05,588 --> 00:02:07,047
It's all about evidence.

35
00:02:08,347 --> 00:02:08,767
Zhang Wei.

36
00:02:09,047 --> 00:02:09,508
Enough.

37
00:02:29,628 --> 00:02:30,108
Zhi Mei,

38
00:02:33,147 --> 00:02:33,628
I'm sorry.

39
00:02:35,348 --> 00:02:37,087
I know I was wrong,

40
00:02:37,348 --> 00:02:39,068
but it's because I care about you too much.

41
00:02:40,487 --> 00:02:42,367
When I saw Zhou Xubai with you,

42
00:02:42,367 --> 00:02:43,848
I was so jealous that I was crazy.

43
00:02:45,908 --> 00:02:46,948
Give me another chance,

44
00:02:48,047 --> 00:02:48,827
just one last time,

45
00:02:50,767 --> 00:02:51,908
and I'll make it up to you.

46
00:02:54,427 --> 00:02:55,267
There's nothing left

47
00:02:56,047 --> 00:02:57,608
for us to lose.

48
00:03:04,047 --> 00:03:06,047
From the moment you chose to lie to me,

49
00:03:06,688 --> 00:03:08,647
you've lost the right

50
00:03:09,188 --> 00:03:10,247
to say sorry.

51
00:03:12,688 --> 00:03:13,468
Dear directors,

52
00:03:14,348 --> 00:03:15,767
let's start now.

53
00:03:23,848 --> 00:03:25,848
Sorry, Director Zhang,

54
00:03:25,848 --> 00:03:27,767
your vote will be canceled.

55
00:03:42,767 --> 00:03:43,288
Zhang Wei,

56
00:03:44,228 --> 00:03:46,728
do you really think you can cover everything up?

57
00:03:48,568 --> 00:03:49,788
This USB drive contains

58
00:03:50,047 --> 00:03:51,888
all the evidence of Zhang Wei's

59
00:03:51,888 --> 00:03:52,968
economic crimes,

60
00:03:53,128 --> 00:03:55,147
embezzlement, and incitement to injury.

61
00:03:56,188 --> 00:03:57,108
As for the complete recording of his own admission

62
00:03:57,108 --> 00:03:58,628
of hiring a hitman,

63
00:03:59,047 --> 00:04:00,068
it has already been handed over to the police.

64
00:04:01,288 --> 00:04:02,147
Everything is there.

65
00:04:07,508 --> 00:04:09,188
What if I can prove my remorse is genuine?

66
00:04:09,188 --> 00:04:09,728
Let go.

67
00:04:10,047 --> 00:04:11,427
I recorded Zhang Wei's evidence.

68
00:04:15,527 --> 00:04:17,448
I recorded Zhang Wei admitting

69
00:04:17,987 --> 00:04:19,587
to instigating me to commit murder for profit.

70
00:04:20,087 --> 00:04:21,267
Regarding your contract killing

71
00:04:22,087 --> 00:04:24,108
and imprisoning me to cause disability,

72
00:04:31,648 --> 00:04:32,867
So,

73
00:04:34,887 --> 00:04:36,947
this is your last card.

74
00:04:41,747 --> 00:04:42,148
Zhimei,

75
00:04:45,047 --> 00:04:46,848
this is the only thing

76
00:04:48,047 --> 00:04:49,507
and the last thing I can do for you.

77
00:04:52,228 --> 00:04:53,047
I'm sorry

78
00:04:53,387 --> 00:04:55,127
for everything I've done before.

79
00:04:56,447 --> 00:04:57,208
And

80
00:05:00,268 --> 00:05:01,067
take care

81
00:05:08,947 --> 00:05:09,747
of yourself.

82
00:05:15,427 --> 00:05:15,708
Wu Xi,

83
00:05:16,528 --> 00:05:18,328
you fickle rascal,

84
00:05:19,047 --> 00:05:20,828
how dare you betray me for the second time!

85
00:05:21,708 --> 00:05:22,487
Zhang Wei,

86
00:05:23,047 --> 00:05:23,528
why?

87
00:05:24,187 --> 00:05:25,427
The Ye family has been good to you.

88
00:05:27,047 --> 00:05:28,447
I treated you like my own brother.

89
00:05:29,047 --> 00:05:29,687
My father

90
00:05:30,348 --> 00:05:31,887
even entrusted you with the legal

91
00:05:31,887 --> 00:05:33,788
and financial power of the group.

92
00:05:35,807 --> 00:05:36,708
Why did you do this?

93
00:05:40,908 --> 00:05:41,307
Why?

94
00:05:42,168 --> 00:05:43,047
My dad

95
00:05:43,288 --> 00:05:44,408
just embezzled

96
00:05:44,408 --> 00:05:45,747
a few million to turn things around,

97
00:05:46,387 --> 00:05:48,208
Your heartless dad

98
00:05:48,208 --> 00:05:49,067
sent him to jail,

99
00:05:49,747 --> 00:05:51,047
and he killed himself.

100
00:05:51,447 --> 00:05:52,528
My mom

101
00:05:53,268 --> 00:05:54,687
died because of this.

102
00:05:55,528 --> 00:05:56,307
You think

103
00:05:56,307 --> 00:05:57,487
you did me a favor

104
00:05:58,047 --> 00:05:59,468
and I should be grateful?

105
00:06:00,927 --> 00:06:01,528
No way!

106
00:06:03,288 --> 00:06:04,387
You owe me!

107
00:06:05,867 --> 00:06:06,887
I'm just taking back

108
00:06:06,887 --> 00:06:08,648
what's mine!

109
00:06:12,807 --> 00:06:13,328
But it's okay.

110
00:06:14,028 --> 00:06:15,148
If I can't have it,

111
00:06:16,447 --> 00:06:17,387
neither can you.

112
00:06:18,507 --> 00:06:19,328
Your trust fund

113
00:06:19,507 --> 00:06:20,708
has been completely drained by me.

114
00:06:21,088 --> 00:06:22,367
Now you're just like me,

115
00:06:22,987 --> 00:06:25,328
with nothing left.

116
00:06:25,747 --> 00:06:27,288
You're so foolish and unaware.

117
00:06:28,328 --> 00:06:30,228
From the moment I suspected you,

118
00:06:30,867 --> 00:06:32,807
the fund data you saw

119
00:06:33,148 --> 00:06:34,268
was nothing but a blockchain illusion

120
00:06:34,268 --> 00:06:35,728
I carefully crafted for you.

121
00:06:35,987 --> 00:06:36,807
You haven't even

122
00:06:37,487 --> 00:06:38,848
touched the real assets.

123
00:06:39,067 --> 00:06:40,348
Impossible.

124
00:06:41,427 --> 00:06:43,067
I successfully withdrew my funds.

125
00:06:43,328 --> 00:06:44,348
What you withdrew

126
00:06:44,668 --> 00:06:46,108
was the marked funds

127
00:06:46,288 --> 00:06:47,487
we prepared for you.

128
00:06:47,747 --> 00:06:48,747
Every transaction

129
00:06:49,387 --> 00:06:51,228
is concrete evidence of your crimes.

130
00:06:53,768 --> 00:06:55,468
This is a trap you set up.

131
00:06:56,148 --> 00:06:57,987
You thought Xu Bai returned to headquarters,

132
00:06:58,228 --> 00:06:59,687
you would have a chance to take advantage.

133
00:06:59,968 --> 00:07:01,168
We just want you

134
00:07:01,168 --> 00:07:02,028
to come out

135
00:07:02,328 --> 00:07:04,047
boldly

136
00:07:04,588 --> 00:07:05,747
for our convenience.

137
00:07:12,867 --> 00:07:13,427
Zhang Wei,

138
00:07:14,108 --> 00:07:15,328
the prison you designed

139
00:07:16,047 --> 00:07:16,768
is trapping

140
00:07:17,288 --> 00:07:18,408
only yourself.

141
00:07:30,927 --> 00:07:33,668
No way!

142
00:07:37,627 --> 00:07:39,528
It's impossible!

143
00:08:10,202 --> 00:08:10,682
Jiayi,

144
00:08:14,002 --> 00:08:15,682
this is a secret world for us.

145
00:08:15,923 --> 00:08:17,202
Let's talk about it tomorrow.

146
00:08:19,882 --> 00:08:21,163
Cheng Jiayi called you,

147
00:08:21,163 --> 00:08:22,163
and you answered.

148
00:08:22,163 --> 00:08:23,442
But when I call,

149
00:08:23,442 --> 00:08:24,642
you're always busy.

150
00:08:25,983 --> 00:08:27,223
Your jealousy

151
00:08:27,223 --> 00:08:28,583
is more refreshing

152
00:08:28,583 --> 00:08:29,762
than the sea breeze.

153
00:08:30,583 --> 00:08:31,382
But,

154
00:08:33,963 --> 00:08:34,923
close your eyes.

155
00:08:37,363 --> 00:08:38,682
It's the red box, right?

156
00:08:39,122 --> 00:08:40,382
I saw it earlier.

157
00:08:42,442 --> 00:08:43,663
You're so annoying.

158
00:08:44,363 --> 00:08:45,023
Stop laughing.

159
00:09:04,742 --> 00:09:05,303
Mr. Zhou,

160
00:09:07,483 --> 00:09:08,943
will you marry me?

161
00:09:10,242 --> 00:09:11,983
I have a lot of money.

162
00:09:12,642 --> 00:09:13,723
I can make you

163
00:09:14,103 --> 00:09:15,742
super happy.

164
00:09:15,882 --> 00:09:17,063
I'm already

165
00:09:17,063 --> 00:09:18,162
the happiest person in the world.

166
00:09:19,583 --> 00:09:20,063
Yes, I will.

167
00:09:25,103 --> 00:09:26,203
You said yes so fast.

168
00:09:28,823 --> 00:09:29,642
I used to be afraid

169
00:09:29,642 --> 00:09:30,583
I would bring you misfortune,

170
00:09:30,963 --> 00:09:32,583
and that you would eventually leave me.

171
00:09:32,823 --> 00:09:33,363
That's why at the beginning...

172
00:09:33,522 --> 00:09:34,262
From now on,

173
00:09:34,422 --> 00:09:35,242
you can love me

174
00:09:35,242 --> 00:09:36,642
in any way you want.

175
00:09:38,323 --> 00:09:39,922
But now...
